To turn this up:

Download VirtualBox and Vagrant.

$ cd ~/c
$ vagrant up


To login:

$ vagrant ssh
foovm$ sudo passwd mohit (Set a password)
foovm$ sudo su - mohit

To shutdown:

$ vagrant halt

To destroy:

$ vagrant destroy

(The next vagrant up will re-provision)

To update:

$ vagrant box update

-------

Provisioning scripts are in bootstrap.sh
